{"tid":1326933,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"19/7深水埗區議會傾反送中同要求成立獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-07-17T11:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T12:03:04.000Z","uid":247608,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"34ffb3541c162650e58f11b1674ad9dfff80cffd","tid":1326933,"uid":247608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:44:42.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲，嚟緊禮拜五19號，深水埗區議會開大會，其中有3項議程同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>反送中/黑警</strong></span>有關，分別係：<br />\n<br />\n建制派動議嘅文件：<span style=\"color: red;\">包容諒解，聆聽尊重，走出對立，重新出發</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L2obv0G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL2obv0G.png&h=800aa007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主派有兩份文件：<br />\n<br />\n1. 由民協譚國僑等人動議<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOnLAtJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOnLAtJ.png&h=90ef0242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 由公民黨伍月蘭動議，民協譚國僑、民主黨袁海文、獨立甄啟榮和議<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ioW08Pm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FioW08Pm.png&h=013a0d8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iqSLAun.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiqSLAun.png&h=f45032f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ybybv2J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fybybv2J.png&h=f023c8e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面三份文件按議程排序，有機會中午時間先會傾到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dCF5AuR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdCF5AuR.png&h=e739aa60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然深水埗建制派夠膽傾反送中同黑警，咁緊係要俾多啲人知道佢地開會講過乜啦，講得衰當然唔可以放過佢地！所以呢，19號見啦！！"},{"pid":"ad218382df5e03a5d6c168e6bbd0b645dd30eada","tid":1326933,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:00:24.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好搞亂個場<br />\n販民堆motion有甄啟榮喺到係夠票過到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而建制嗰條motion唔夠票過"},{"pid":"b3096fc8f78e4444c07dbc7d69ebc48d67ca61bc","tid":1326933,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:03:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}